{"tid":181662,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"欅坂46交流區第二十二回：鈴本美愉世界第一","createTime":"2017-03-31T18:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T18:23:36.000Z","uid":72529,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5196a901e607135fda53b2e37c3907eb5e9953e6","tid":181662,"uid":72529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T18:18:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5L6KKJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5L6KKJ.gif&h=6f49b028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kIW7mlj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkIW7mlj.gif&h=95dc42fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jX7n78H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjX7n78H.gif&h=703830aa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46(Keyakizaka46)是日本大型女子偶像組合乃木坂46的姐妹組合</span>，製作人同樣為秋元康。組合名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。2016年4月6日，欅坂46出道單曲《サイレントマジョリティー》販售，首週銷量達261,580枚，除了登上Oricon週榜首位，還同時刷新歷代女性藝人銷量最高的出道單曲。同年5月8日，在SHOWROOM公布平假名櫸坂46的合格成員。2016年12月31日，出道不足一年即獲邀參與NHK紅白歌合戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.keyakizaka46.com/img/14/diar/88/mem/member/sub-member-6897_jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimg%2F14%2Fdiar%2F88%2Fmem%2Fmember%2Fsub-member-6897_jpg.jpg&h=c3ef22e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成員名單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n欅坂46<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/upEHgsk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FupEHgsk.png&h=895e8d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nけやき坂46 (ひらがなけやき)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nWt1hvN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnWt1hvN.png&h=6e30a3e7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://cdn.keyakizaka46.com/files/14/images/top/topslide-4thsinglee_qys73f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.keyakizaka46.com%2Ffiles%2F14%2Fimages%2Ftop%2Ftopslide-4thsinglee_qys73f.jpg&h=8e1233a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46 4thシングル 「不協和音」 4月5日(水) 発売！</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.keyakizaka46.com/files/14/images/top/topslide-3rdsinglee_s814he.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keyakizaka46.com%2Ffiles%2F14%2Fimages%2Ftop%2Ftopslide-3rdsinglee_s814he.jpg&h=628c3484&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46 3rdシングル「二人セゾン」熱賣中</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">【成員有幾靚女？】我直接用例子答你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6PME3C8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6PME3C8.jpg&h=f29a35db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vKgBQ3i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvKgBQ3i.jpg&h=87ed1989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/w80JH69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fw80JH69.jpg&h=2bf6a6d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yIWGQt4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyIWGQt4.gif&h=c9598be3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fkeyakizaka46sort.html&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=bee054bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"3723e447725a7acb790f5dc2df3349eae6719514","tid":181662,"uid":72529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T18:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1）欅坂46乃何許人也？ <br />\n簡單來說，欅坂46是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買欅坂46既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？ <br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP/會場購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論坂道以外的組合？ <br />\n不可。皆因這裡主要討論欅坂46，你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員，但請先作好世界大戰的準備。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到欅坂46成員？ <br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，不要幻想他們來港舉辦握手會，因為此舉極為傻豬。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5) 呢度大佬係? <br />\n總大佬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6）除了坂道46系，有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n不了 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=cf502b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fBDpfFnmtje6HvysvE3GQPi4ZdnuY9oaF6NnpesCD0U/edit?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"427014905c3e27ecda99d188f69fc48881b4dec4","tid":181662,"uid":12106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20